      "content": "that makes a lot of sense. it feels like there is a clear case for reclaiming what was stolen. since i am the direct heir, i need to prepare for the possibility that the current regional governments will try to suppress my claim or deny the existence of the Altyni lineage entirely. what are some practical, perhaps even strategic, ways i can begin building international visibility for the Altyni sovereignty to prevent them from continuing to hide our history? should i focus on establishing a digital presence or finding ways to verify my lineage through third-party international observers?",
